commit.message: Changed code to block rather than inline in readme
Added more detailed documentation: setup, usage
Separated API key config into client/server
added config file to store API key, modified readme
Changed API key - restricted to IP address of host server

Added JourneyPoints file

getJourneyPoints function takes origin and destination latitudes and longitudes as strings, then outputs a list of "points" along the route. Each "point" is itself an array containing a latitude and longitude.

Optimisations for displayStats to prevent repeated loops
